column16: Yunel Escobar grounds into a force out, third baseman Placido Polanco to second baseman Derek Dietrich.   Jose Molina out at 2nd.
Jose Molina singles on a sharp line drive to left fielder Chris Coghlan.
James Loney pops out to second baseman Derek Dietrich.
Evan Longoria out on a sacrifice fly to center fielder Justin Ruggiano.   Ben Zobrist scores.    Matt Joyce to 3rd.
Kelly Johnson singles on a soft fly ball to center fielder Justin Ruggiano.   Ben Zobrist to 3rd.    Matt Joyce to 2nd.
Ben Revere singles on a soft ground ball to pitcher Duane Below.   Jimmy Rollins to 2nd.
Jimmy Rollins singles on a line drive to shortstop Adeiny Hechavarria, deflected by pitcher Duane Below.
Tyler Cloyd grounds out softly to first baseman Greg Dobbs.
Duane Below intentionally walks Erik Kratz.
Domonic Brown grounds out softly, second baseman Derek Dietrich to first baseman Greg Dobbs.   Ryan Howard scores.    Delmon Young to 3rd.
Delmon Young doubles (4) on a sharp fly ball to center fielder Chris Coghlan.   Ryan Howard to 3rd.
Ryan Howard singles on a sharp line drive to right fielder Marcell Ozuna.
